Shelley Longworth https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shelley_Longworth 0 Shelley Nicola Longworth (born 22 March 1976) is an English comedy actress and voice over artist. She is best known for playing the role of Sam Wood in Benidorm, from 2011 to 2012 and from 2017 to 2018.
